1. *Planiraš* li da ideš na odmor ove godine? (Are you planning to go on vacation this year?)
2. Ove godine *planiraš* odmor, zar ne? (You're planning a vacation this year, right?)
3. Kako *planiraš* da ostvariš svoje ciljeve? (How do you plan to achieve your goals?)
4. Ne mogu da verujem da već *planiraš* svoj rođendan za sledeću godinu. (I can't believe you're already planning your birthday for next year.)
5. *Planiraš* li da se preseliš u inostranstvo? (Are you planning to move abroad?)
6. Da li si *planirao* svoj budžet za ovaj mesec? (Have you planned your budget for this month?)
7. Šta si *planirao* da radiš danas? (What did you plan to do today?)
8. Ona *planira* da studira medicinu na fakultetu. (She plans to study medicine at university.)
9. Šef nam *planira* veliki sastanak za naredni mesec. (Our boss is planning a big meeting for next month.)
10. *Planiraju* da renoviraju kuću tokom leta. (They are planning to renovate their house during the summer.)